---
import lismyhero from '../images/lismy-hero.jpg'
---
<section class="hero w-full flex flex-col  h-[667px] items-center justify-end lg:mt-10">
    <img src={lismyhero.src} alt="lismy hero" class="lg:absolute w-full h-full object-cover">
    <div class="relative lg:w-1/3 lg:mb-28 lg:mx-[20%] space-y-2 flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-slate-500 p-6 text-center bg-opacity-50 lg:rounded-2xl lg:mt-10">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">¡Dale Vida a Tus Manos!</h1>
        <p class="text-white font-semibold" >Descubre una experiencia de manicure excepcional que transformará tus uñas en verdaderas obras de arte. ¡Haz que tus manos y pies brillen con Elegancia y Glamour!</p>
        <button class="text-white border-2 border-white font-bold bg-pink-500 p-4 lg:w-[50%] rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-all">BOOK NOW</button>
    </div>
</section>

